&lt;p&gt;Read the following statements about derivational morphemes and choose the correct option:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(A) Normalize and courageous are derivational morphemes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(B) Derivational morphemes are used to show some aspect of the grammatical function of a word.&lt;/p&gt;
